'''歐克西亞高原'''（'''Oxia Planum'''）是一個位於[[火星|火星]]的高原。該高原被選定為[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]][[ExoMars|ExoMars]]計畫的{{link-en|ExoMars (火星車)|ExoMars (rover)|火星車}}登陸地點<ref name="BBC-20151021">{{cite news |last=Amos |first=Jonathan |title=ExoMars rover: Landing preference is for Oxia Planum |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-34584214 |date=October 21, 2015 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |accessdate=October 22, 2015 |archive-date=2017-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428083406/http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-34584214 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="UT-20151021">{{cite web |last=Atkinson |first=Nancy |title=Scientists Want ExoMars Rover to Land at Oxia Planum |url=http://www.universetoday.com/123018/scientists-want-exomars-rover-to-land-at-oxia-planum/ |date=October 21, 2015 |work=[[Universe_Today|Universe Today]] |accessdate=October 22, 2015 |archive-date=2019-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601193222/https://www.universetoday.com/123018/scientists-want-exomars-rover-to-land-at-oxia-planum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該地點低於火星大地水準面超過3000公尺<ref>[http://www.planetary.org/blogs/emily-lakdawalla/2015/11041714-esa-mission-updates.html ESA mission updates] {{Wayback|url=http://www.planetary.org/blogs/emily-lakdawalla/2015/11041714-esa-mission-updates.html |date=20160514070818 }}. Emily Lakdawalla; 5 November 2015.</ref>。

==概要==
歐克西亞高原是火星表面暴露黏土岩層範圍最大的區域之一，表面岩層年齡約39億年<ref name='clay'>{{cite news |last=Durnham |first=R. |url=http://redplanet.asu.edu/?p=15954 |title=ExoMars 2018 rover heading for Oxia Planum |work=Red Planet Report |date=October 21, 2015 |accessdate=October 22, 2015 |archive-date=2016-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616180818/http://redplanet.asu.edu/?p=15954 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該區域有富含鐵和鎂的[[黏土|黏土]]礦物，代表當地曾經有[[火星水文|大量液態水]]存在。該區域位於一系列峽谷之中，表面暴露的岩層顯示了不同地質時間下各自相異的沉積岩層，可表示不同水量的各時期下各種沉積狀態。

歐克西亞高原中的黏土沉積可能位於殘餘的[[沖積扇|沖積扇]]或[[三角洲|三角洲]]表面以下，接近[[庫貢谷|庫貢谷]]（Coogoon Vallis）的出口；這樣的環境可能保留了[[生命印迹|生命印迹]]，不使其受到火星表面強烈輻射和高度氧化環境所破壞<ref name='clay'/><ref name="UdL-20140514">{{cite web |url=http://marsnext.jpl.nasa.gov/workshops/2014_05/14_Oxia_Thollot_webpage.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |title=Oxia Planum, landing site for Mars 2020 |last=Thollot |first=P. |last2=Quantin |first2=C. |date=May 14, 2014 |work=Universite de Lion, France |accessdate=October 22, 2015 |archive-date=2016-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603000809/http://marsnext.jpl.nasa.gov/workshops/2014_05/14_Oxia_Thollot_webpage.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="UA-20141001">{{cite web |author=Staff |url=http://www.uahirise.org/ESP_037070_1985 |title=Possible Future Mars Landing Site in Oxia Planum - ''High Resolution Imaging Science Experiment'' |work=[[亞利桑那大學|The University of Arizona]] |date=October 1, 2014 |accessdate=October 21, 2015 |archive-date=2016-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512112004/http://www.uahirise.org/ESP_037070_1985 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
